OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FBritish Transport Police (BTP)
OL,7,Fofficers who went on a two-hour kebab
OL,8,Fbreak on the night of the attack have
OL,9,Fbeen handed final written warnings.
OL,11,FFive BTP officers were policing the
OL,12,Fconcert that night, with officers
OL,13,Finstructed by their sergeant to ensure
OL,14,Fat least one was present in the City
OL,15,FRoom when the concert ended.
OL,17,FBut when a PC and a PCSO went on a 10-
OL,18,Fmile round trip to a takeaway in
OL,19,FLongsight, south Manchester, they
OL,20,Ffailed to follow orders.
