OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FThe Manchester Arena Inquiry had heard
OL,7,Fthat suicide bomber Salman Abedi may
OL,8,Fhave been challenged if a (BTP)
OL,9,Fofficer had been present.
OL,11,FAn investigation into the BTP officers
OL,12,Fwas launched following a complaint by
OL,13,Ffamilies of the victims relating to
OL,14,Fevidence heard at the inquiry.
OL,16,FA report by Sir John Saunders,
OL,17,Fchairman of the inquiry, into security
OL,18,Farrangements at the venue concluded
OL,19,Fthere were "significant failures" by
OL,20,Fall five BTP officers on duty at the
OL,21,Farena on May 22, 2017.
