OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FAt 7:27pm, a Police Constable and a
OL,7,FPCSO colleague drove five miles from
OL,8,FVictoria Station to south Manchester
OL,9,Fto get a kebab, and were off duty for
OL,10,Ftwo hours and nine minutes, the
OL,11,Finquiry heard.
OL,13,FIt meant that when Abedi made his
OL,14,F"final approach" to the City Room,
OL,15,Fdressed all in black and walking
OL,16,Falmost bent double, carrying his heavy
OL,17,Frucksack bomb, no officers were
OL,18,Fpatrolling the area around the arena.
