OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FIf a BTP officer had been present,
OL,7,FAbedi may have been challenged after a
OL,8,Fmember of the public, Christopher
OL,9,FWild, reported his concerns to Showsec
OL,10,Fstewards about half an hour before the
OL,11,Fexplosion, the inquiry was told.
OL,13,FThe same officers were praised for
OL,14,Ftheir response after the blast `
OL,15,Frunning into the City Room foyer to
OL,16,Fhelp those injured.
