OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FThe (IOPC) directed an investigation
OL,7,Finto the actions of two police
OL,8,Fconstables and two police community
OL,9,Fsupport officers (PCSOs) who were
OL,10,Fresponsible for patrolling the arena
OL,11,Fon the night of the attack in 2017.
OL,13,FThey found one of the police officers
OL,14,Fand one of the PCSOs, who is now
OL,15,Femployed as a BTP police constable,
OL,16,Fshould be disciplined for the "timing
OL,17,Fand length of their refreshment
OL,18,Fbreaks", as well as failing to follow
OL,19,Finstructions from a senior officer.
