OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FA misconduct meeting found the case
OL,7,Fproven against both individuals.
OL,9,FThey were given final written warnings
OL,10,Fwhich will remain in force for the
OL,11,Fnext two years.
OL,13,FThe police watchdog also recommended
OL,14,FBTP apologises to the families of the
OL,15,Fvictims for the shortcomings in the
OL,16,Fpolicing operation on the night.
OL,18,FThis was accepted by the force, the
OL,19,FIOPC said.
