OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FThe watchdog found "no persuasive
OL,7,Fevidence" to suggest longer breaks had
OL,8,Falso been taken at other Arena events.
OL,10,FThe evidence "showed BTP officers were
OL,11,Fgiven clear instructions about the
OL,12,Flengths of refreshment breaks," the
OL,13,FIOPC said.
