OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,FIOPC regional director Mel Palmer
OL,7,Fadded: "Nothing can bring back the
OL,8,Flives lost, or make up for the pain
OL,9,Fand suffering experienced by the
OL,10,Fbereaved, but it is important that the
OL,11,Factions of the police are thoroughly
OL,12,Fscrutinised, mistakes are acknowledged
OL,13,Fand lessons are learned.
OL,15,F"That is why we have carefully
OL,16,Freviewed the steps taken by BTP to
OL,17,Faddress the areas for improvement
OL,18,Fidentified in the inquiry report, and
OL,19,Falso recommended that the force
OL,20,Fapologises to the complainants.
