OL,3,CWarning for police officers who went
OL,4,Cfor kebab on night of arena attack
OL,6,F"This investigation has also ensured
OL,7,Fthe two individuals whose actions fell
OL,8,Fbelow the standards expected by the
OL,9,Fpublic, and who ignored instructions
OL,10,Ffrom a senior officer, have now been
OL,11,Fheld accountable."
OL,13,FAnother BTP officer who was the
OL,14,Fsubject of the complaint retired
OL,15,Fbefore the investigation began.
OL,17,F"We reached the view that the evidence
OL,18,Findicated there would have been no
OL,19,Fcase to answer for either misconduct
OL,20,For gross misconduct, had they still
OL,21,Fbeen serving," the IOPC said.
